examples.bad:
DocumentBuilderFactory dbf = DocumentBuilderFactory.newInstance();
dbf.setFeature("http://apache.org/xml/features/nonvalidating/load-external-dtd", true); // BAD: allows external DTDs
DocumentBuilder db = dbf.newDocumentBuilder();
Document doc = db.parse(input);

examples.good:
DocumentBuilderFactory dbf = DocumentBuilderFactory.newInstance();
dbf.setFeature("http://apache.org/xml/features/nonvalidating/load-external-dtd", false); // GOOD: disables external DTDs
DocumentBuilder db = dbf.newDocumentBuilder();
Document doc = db.parse(input);
